地呢場運動 <br />\n 📍主打活動內容: <br />\n1.社工輔導 @SkyBlueVK (contact)<br />\n2.十年/港台鏗鏘集放映會<br />\n3. 公民廣場自由發言: 不合作運動如何升級? <br />\n4.法律知識教教你<br />\n5.職工盟TALK: 何謂無限期罷工"},{"pid":"767d6a4f4334f27e57fe2ddbf355bda05447eaea","tid":1395853,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7da0db8b023b1f867b63518029bcf422fc1badc","tid":1395853,"uid":138163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"荃灣公園對住臭海皮，沙咀道求場唔好咩？夠開揚喎，8月5日罷罷罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394389646ac0ac3833b04f2c485a23bb2a72d3f7","tid":1395853,"uid":138163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7da0db8b023b1f867b63518029bcf422fc1badc","tid":1395853,"uid":138163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"荃灣公園對住臭海皮，沙咀道求場唔好咩？夠開揚喎，8月5日罷罷罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:20:14.000Z","msg":"屌，手快打錯字，沙咀道球場"},{"pid":"e3088a2904a50403806d798755c0c3131b983399","tid":1395853,"uid":142857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7da0db8b023b1f867b63518029bcf422fc1badc","tid":1395853,"uid":138163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"荃灣公園對住臭海皮，沙咀道求場唔好咩？夠開揚喎，8月5日罷罷罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:21:21.000Z","msg":"屌其實都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />臭到仆街"},{"pid":"333c99b43a688b63cd31dbace6410f51ca2302e3","tid":1395853,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:29:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">荃灣公園<br />\n荃灣西鐵站附近</span>"},{"pid":"49565bb22c8c7d9023281d435b28069fe4de13c0","tid":1395853,"uid":161098,"like